{"body":"### Discovery ignores context cancel

**Medium Severity**

<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->
After fetch, `discoverReachable` walks every object without checking `ctx`. Cancelling the command during discovery on a large repo keeps running until the walk finishes, even though translation already honors cancellation.
<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->

